<b>Bill Gates</b>, Chairman and CEO, Microsoft Corp.<BR>
Wednesday, January 5, 7:00-8:00pm<HR width=75% align="left" noshade>
Microsoft's vision is to enable consumers to access the information and entertainment they care about whenever and wherever they want to.  Microsoft's continued efforts in connecting smart digital appliances together, providing underlying technologies for both personal computers and consumer devices, and providing information and entertainment services to help make this vision a reality.  Under Bill Gates' leadership, Microsoft has become the world's leading provider of software that helps make peoples lives better.



		
