<img src="../../Graphics/Conf/keynote/benhamou.jpg" width=72 height=83 alt="" border="0" align="left" hspace=10 vspace=5><b>Eric A. Benhamou</b>, Chairman and CEO, 3Com Corp.<BR>
Thursday, January 6, 8:30-10:00am<HR width=75% noshade align="left">

As we move into the new millennium, the constant flow of information shows no
signs of slowing down.  How will that information integrate into our daily
lives?  That's the theme behind Eric Benhamou's address.  At the helm of 3Com,
Mr. Benhamou is in a unique position to present some answers.  Since 3Com is one
of the few companies enabling a more connected lifestyle, it's safe to assume
Mr. Benhamou will share some unique insights.


		
