Thursday, January 6, 4:00-5:30pm<HR width=75% noshade align="left">

Information technology and home networking are vital components of CES, and Sun Microsystems has been an innovator in both. Scott McNealy's global company offers end-to-end solutions for doing business in the network age. With its platform-independent Java&trade; and Jini&trade; technologies, Sun provides high-speed microprocessors, scalable systems, robust software, network storage, mission-critical support and comprehensive professional services&#151;all the key components that drive the Internet as well as corporate intranets and business-to-business extranets. 


		
